channel.title: Down Factor
channel.description:
Does anyone here like Down Factor? It is one of my favorite bands, but they aren't very well known.
(Their songs are pretty brutal)
Heres their website: [url=http://downfactor.com]http://downfactor.com[/url]
Heres some samples of their songs: [url=http://www.audiolunchbox.com/album?a=48343]http://www.audiolunchbox.com/album?a=48343[/url]
My favorite songs are "Blinded", "Seethe", and "The Root of all Evil".
